        public NamedBean<DerivePath> createPathDeriver(String rootName,
                                               String regEx)
                                        throws BeanMisconfiguredException
        Creates a (rooted) file-path generator for a rootName and a regEx which matches three groups The first group should correspond to top-level folder for the project The second group should correspond to the unique name of the dataset. The third group should correspond to the unique name of the experiment.
        Parameters:
        rootName - if non-empty (and non-null) a rooted derivePath is created instead of a non rooted
        regEx -
        Returns:
        Throws:
